1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper discusses the use of point clouds in 3D object representation, which is a common topic in computer vision. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper proposes a point cloud simplification algorithm, which is a common topic in graphics. 
3. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The paper deals with processing large-scale point clouds, which is a common topic in computational geometry. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses 3D immersive tele-presence, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses graph spectral processing and graph filters, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning.
